<view class="page safe-bottom">
  <view class="eyebrow">LEGAL</view>
  <view class="title-xl">{{title}}</view>
  <view class="section panel">
    <view class="legal-line" wx:for="{{items}}" wx:key="index">
      <view class="dot"></view>
      <view class="body">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="section panel-quiet">
    <view class="title-md">AI 辅助说明</view>
    <view class="body">原点智学只提供学习建议、作业优先级和思路提示；不替代学校教学、老师判断或家长监护，不提供作业代写服务。</view>
  </view>
  <view class="section panel-quiet compliance-note">
    <view class="title-md">服务边界</view>
    <view class="body">本版本不提供学科培训课程、直播或录播授课、教师一对一辅导、考试押题、拍照搜题出结果或学习结果承诺；仅围绕用户主动输入的学校作业和卡点，提供学习过程建议。</view>
  </view>
  <view class="section panel-quiet legal-depth-card" wx:if="{{surfaceDepthPack}}">
    <view class="title-md">{{surfaceDepthPack.title}}</view>
    <view class="body">{{surfaceDepthPack.summary}}</view>
    <view class="legal-depth-list">
      <button class="legal-depth-chip {{item.ready ? 'ready' : ''}}" wx:for="{{surfaceDepthPack.cards}}" wx:key="id" data-route="{{item.route}}" data-dimension-id="{{item.id}}" data-label="{{item.displayLabel}}" bindtap="runSurfaceDepthAction">
        {{item.displayLabel}}
      </button>
    </view>
    <view class="body">{{surfaceDepthPack.familyLine}}</view>
  </view>
</view>
